         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Diogenes to Sarapion, his most honoured, greetings. As you told me about the . . . there are 8 female and 8 male. The sheep are in good condition. As from the 21st one workman came to me. If you have green fodder for sale do not sell it because ours [- - -]</ab>
